 <h2>Structured Data</h2>

 <p>
 As the
 Web grows to include a variety of data producers, data sources, and 
 mashup applications it becomes increasingly important to enable user agents 
 to recognize and process the data that is inherently embedded in HTML 
 documents.
 This specification enables the markup of structured data with the HTML5
 language using a number of techniques described below.
 </p>

